OL,12,G1720 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FThe B&Bers meet for the last time
OL,14,     Fto settle some scores. There's
OL,15,     Fbeef about breakfast and tabletop
OL,16,     Ftroubles, and Derek discusses his
OL,17,     Fslumber sorrows. Which B&B has won
OL,18,     Fthe week?
